@startuml UC10_Sequence
title UC10: 修改成绩 - 顺序图

actor "教师" as Teacher
boundary "成绩修改界面" as EditForm
control "成绩控制类" as GradeCtrl
entity "Grade" as Grade

Teacher -> EditForm : 修改特定学生的分数
EditForm -> GradeCtrl : updateGrade(studentId, newScores)
GradeCtrl -> Grade : checkAuditStatus()
Grade --> GradeCtrl : notAuditYet

GradeCtrl -> Grade : update(newScores)
Grade --> GradeCtrl : updatedOverall
GradeCtrl --> EditForm : 提示修改成功
EditForm -> Teacher : 显示结果
@enduml
